OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FQari Asim: Imam removed as 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fgovernment adviser over    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ffilm protests              
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, An imam has been dismissed as a        
OL,6, government adviser after backing calls 
OL,7, for a film about the Prophet Mohammed's
OL,8, daughter to be banned.                 
OL,10,FQari Asim, 44, was removed from his    
OL,11,Frole as an Islamophobia consultant     
OL,12,Fafter protests against the film The    
OL,13,FLady of Heaven.                        
OL,15,FSupporting the campaign "to limit free 
OL,16,Fexpression" precluded him from         
OL,17,Fcontinuing, the government said.       
OL,19,FMr Asim was appointed MBE in 2012 for  
OL,20,Fbuilding "community harmony" in Leeds. 
